[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"An GitOps and ArgoCD based Kubernetes Expert AI Agent specializing in cluster operations, troubleshooting, and maintenance.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"image\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
