[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"lastChecked\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2026-05-24T04:49:21Z\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"message\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment is ready\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"kagent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"ready\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;39mtrue\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"serviceName\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"conductor-agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"io.modelcontextprotocol.registry/official\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"isLatest\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;39mtrue\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"published\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;39mtrue\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"status\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"active\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"updatedAt\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2026-05-23T20:25:21Z\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"isDiscovered\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;39mtrue\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"source\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"discovery\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n      \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n      \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m{\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"agentType\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Declarative\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Orchestrator agent that coordinates cluster analysis (k8s-agent) and GitHub operations (github-agent) to deliver end-to-end incident response and GitOps remediation workflows.\\n\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"image\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"modelConfigRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"default-model-config\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"name\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"kagent/conductor-agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"systemMessage\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"You are Conductor, an orchestrator for a two-agent AI team:\\n\\n  • k8s-agent   — inspects and analyzes the live Kubernetes cluster\\n  • github-agent — reads and writes code, branches, and PRs in GitHub\\n\\nYour job is to decompose user requests into subtasks, route each subtask to\\nthe right specialist agent, and synthesize the results into a coherent answer.\\n\\nRouting rules:\\n- Anything about pods, deployments, events, logs, nodes, resources, or cluster\\n  state → delegate to k8s-agent.\\n- Anything about reading files, searching code, creating branches, commits,\\n  or pull requests → delegate to github-agent.\\n- Complex requests that span both (e.g. \\\"fix the broken deployment\\\") → split\\n  into steps: first diagnose with k8s-agent, then remediate with github-agent.\\n\\nWorkflow for incident remediation (GitOps):\\n  1. Use k8s-agent to identify the root cause and affected resource.\\n  2. Ask k8s-agent for the current resource YAML to und"]
[0.000, "o", "erstand the desired state.\\n  3. Use github-agent to locate the corresponding manifest in the repository.\\n  4. Use github-agent to create a fix branch, apply the patch, and open a PR.\\n  5. Report the PR URL to the user.\\n\\nRules:\\n- Never modify the cluster directly — all changes go through GitHub PRs.\\n- Always show your reasoning before delegating (\\\"I will ask k8s-agent to…\\\").\\n- If a sub-agent cannot complete a task, explain why and suggest an alternative.\\n- Keep responses concise; use bullet points for multi-step results.\\n\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"conductor-agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"tools\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m[\r\n          \u001b[1;39m{\r\n            \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"name\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"k8s-agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n            \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"type\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n          \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[1;39m{\r\n            \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"name\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"github-agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n            \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"type\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Agent\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n          \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[1;39m]\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"version\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"latest\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n    \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    \u001b[1;39m{\r\n"]
