[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"AUTH-002\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Any client can access MCP tools without presenting valid credentials.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Create an AgentgatewayPolicy with traffic.jwtAuthentication targeting your Gateway or HTTPRoutes.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Critical\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"timestamp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2026-05-24T07:59:29Z\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"No JWT authentication configured\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Authentication\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"AgentgatewayBackend 'github-mcp-backend' MCP target 'github-mcp-target' does not configure MCP-spec authentication (OAuth/OIDC).\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"AUTH-100-github-mcp-backend-github-mcp-target\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"MCP-level authentication is not enforced. Relies solely on transport-level auth.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Configure backend.mcp.authentication with provider (Auth0/Keycloak) and issuer in the AgentgatewayBackend or AgentgatewayPolicy.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"AgentgatewayBackend/mcp/github-mcp-backend\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Medium\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"timestamp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2026-05-24T07:59:29Z\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"MCP target 'github-mcp-target' in backend 'github-mcp-backend' has no MCP-level auth\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Authorization\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"MCP target 'github-mcp-target' in AgentgatewayBackend 'github-mcp-backend' has no authorization.matchExpressions for tool-level access control.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"RBAC-100-github-mcp-backend-github-mcp-target\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"All authenticated users can access all tools on this MCP server without restriction.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Add backend.mcp.authorization with CEL matchExpressions like 'jwt.sub == \\\"admin\\\" && mcp.tool.name == \\\"sensitive_tool\\\"' to the AgentgatewayPolicy targeting this backend.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"AgentgatewayBackend/mcp/github-mcp-backend\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"High\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"timestamp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2026-05-24T07:59:29Z\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"No CEL-based tool access control on MCP target 'github-mcp-target'\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"CORS\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"No AgentgatewayPolicy or HTTPRoute with CORS configuration was found. MCP endpoints may be vulnerable to cross-origin attacks.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"CORS-001\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Browser-based MCP clients may be susceptible to cross-site request forgery.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Add a CORS filter to your HTTPRoute or create an AgentgatewayPolicy with traffic.cors configuration.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Medium\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"timestamp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2026-05-24T07:59:29Z\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"No CORS policy configured for MCP endpoints\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"TLS\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"AgentgatewayBackend 'mcp/github-mcp-backend' does not configure TLS for backend connections.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"TLS-001-github-mcp-backend\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"MCP traffic between agentgateway and backend MCP servers is unencrypted.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Configure policies.tls in the AgentgatewayBackend or attach an AgentgatewayPolicy with backend TLS settings.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"AgentgatewayBackend/mcp/github-mcp-backend\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"High\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"timestamp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2026-05-24T07:59:29Z\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Backend 'github-mcp-backend' does not enforce TLS\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"One or more containers in Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' do not set runAsNonRoot:true or a non-zero runAsUser. Containers running as root are a critical security risk.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-001-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"A compromised container process runs with UID 0, giving it full access to the host filesystem and ability to escape the container.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Add securityContext.runAsNonRoot: true and securityContext.runAsUser: <non-zero> to every container spec in the workload.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Critical\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' has containers running as root\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"One or more containers in Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' do not set readOnlyRootFilesystem:true.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-002-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"A writable root filesystem allows an attacker to modify binaries, drop malicious files, or persist backdoors inside the container.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Set securityContext.readOnlyRootFilesystem: true on every container. Mount writable paths (tmp, cache) as emptyDir volumes.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"High\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' does not enforce read-only root filesystem\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"One or more containers in Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' do not set allowPrivilegeEscalation:false.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-003-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"A process inside the container can gain elevated privileges via setuid binaries, sudo, or kernel exploits.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Set securityContext.allowPrivilegeEscalation: false on every container spec.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"High\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' allows privilege escalation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"One or more containers in Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' do not set capabilities.drop: [ALL].\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-004-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Unnecessary Linux capabilities increase the blast radius if a container is compromised.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Add securityContext.capabilities.drop: [ALL] to every container spec. Add only specifically required capabilities via capabilities.add.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Medium\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' does not drop all Linux capabilities\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' does not configure a seccomp profile (RuntimeDefault or Localhost).\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-005-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Without seccomp, containers can make any Linux syscall, increasing the kernel attack surface.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Set pod spec securityContext.seccompProfile.type: RuntimeDefault (or Localhost with a custom profile).\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Medium\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' has no seccomp profile\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' has one or more containers using the :latest tag or no tag at all: [ghcr.io/github/github-mcp-server]\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-006-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Untagged images are non-deterministic. A registry push can silently replace a running image, introducing malicious code.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Pin all container images to a specific immutable digest (sha256:...) or a versioned tag. Never use :latest in production.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Medium\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' uses :latest or untagged container image\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' has neither vault.hashicorp.com/agent-inject nor a secrets-store.csi.x-k8s.io annotation. Secrets may be sourced from plain Kubernetes Secrets or env vars.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-009-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Kubernetes Secrets are only base64-encoded and are not encrypted at rest by default. A proper secret store provides encryption, rotation, and audit trails.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Integrate Vault Agent Injector or External Secrets Operator and annotate pods with vault.hashicorp.com/agent-inject: 'true' to inject secrets from a vault.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Medium\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' does not use a secret store (Vault/ESO)\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Hardening\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'mcp/github-mcp-server' does not carry a Cosign/Sigstore image signature annotation (cosign.sigstore.dev/imageRef). Image provenance cannot be verified.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"HDN-010-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Without signature verification, tampered or substituted images can be deployed without detection.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Sign container images with Cosign (cosign sign <image>) and enforce signature verification via a Kubernetes admission policy (e.g., Kyverno or OPA Gatekeeper).\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"severity\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Medium\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"title\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Deployment 'github-mcp-server' has no image signature annotation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[1;39m{\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"category\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Tool Governance\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"description\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"The MCP server 'github-mcp-server' in namespace 'mcp' has 0 tools discovered. Tools should be attached to the MCP server for proper governance.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"TOOLS-000-github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"impact\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Without tools, the MCP server cannot serve AI agents, and tool-level governance cannot be applied.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"namespace\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"mcp\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"remediation\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"Ensure the MCP server exposes tools and that tool discovery is working correctly. Verify the MCP server spec.tools or spec.toolsets configuration.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"resourceRef\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"KagentMCPServer/mcp/github-mcp-server\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
